Fixed DB lock contention on worker_status and worker_runs writes. Added comprehensive retry-with-exponential-backoff to status.py GET /api/status/overview endpoint (queries WorkerRun, AgentStatus, Memory, InboxItem tables). Created reusable db_retry utility module (execute_with_retry, query_with_retry, commit_with_retry) for consistent retry patterns across codebase. Database already configured with WAL mode and 30s busy_timeout. All 32 worker/status/db_retry tests passing.
